Quote:  <i>flax lily n</i> 1 : NEW ZEALAND FLAX 2 : any of several plants constituting a genus (<i>Dianella</i>) of the family Liliaceae; esp : an Australian plant (<i>D. laevis</i>) that yields a long silky fiber formerly used by the aborigines for making baskets
